high_descs: Turn around and head to the counter next to the stove top.
Pick up the spoon on the right side of the stove.
Turn around and move across the room to the microwave cart on your right.
Put the spoon on top of the apple on the left side of the microwave.
Turn around and move to the counter above the mini fridge on your right.
Pick up the spoon in front of the toaster from the counter.
Turn right and head back to the microwave cart on your right.
Put the second spoon on top of the apple on the left side of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons on top of the apple next to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the spoon between the pepper mill and the spatula.
Turn around and walk over to the table with the microwave oven.
Set the spoon vertically against the tomato with the handle side down.
Turn right and walk over to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the spoon in front of the toaster.
Turn right and walk back to the table with the microwave oven.
Set the spoon vertically with the handle side down to the left of the first spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place two spoons upright on the table with the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the counter, turn left, go to the stove
Pick up the spoon to the right of the stove on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the spoon to the left of the microwave
Turn right and go to the stove, turn right, go forward
Pick up the spoon on the counter
Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the microwave
Put the spoon to the left of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons beside the microwave
